#standardSQL
CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE
 ${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_analytics_session_data AS
WITH
 visitor_page_content AS (
 SELECT
   fullVisitorID,
   (LEAD(hits.time, 1)
     OVER (PARTITION BY fullVisitorId ORDER BY hits.time ASC) - hits.time)
             AS session_duration
 FROM
   `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.${targetTable}`,
   UNNEST(hits) AS hits
 GROUP BY
   fullVisitorId,
   hits.time )
 # aggregate web stats
SELECT
 fullVisitorID AS visitorId,
 SUM(session_duration) AS session_duration
FROM
 visitor_page_content
GROUP BY
 fullVisitorID
HAVING
 session_duration > 0

#standardSQL
CREATE OR REPLACE MODEL ${bqDataset}.df_ga_time_series_model
OPTIONS
 (model_type = 'ARIMA',
  time_series_timestamp_col = 'parsed_date',
  time_series_data_col = 'total_visits',
  auto_arima = TRUE,
  data_frequency = 'AUTO_FREQUENCY'
) AS
SELECT
 PARSE_TIMESTAMP("%Y%m%d", date) AS parsed_date,
 SUM(totals.visits) AS total_visits
FROM
 `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.${targetTable}`
GROUP BY date
union all
SELECT
 PARSE_TIMESTAMP("%Y%m%d", date) AS parsed_date,
 SUM(totals.visits) AS total_visits
FROM
 `bigquery-public-data.google_analytics_sample.ga_sessions_*`
GROUP BY date limit 3

#standardSQL
CREATE OR REPLACE TABLE `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_forecast` AS
SELECT
  history_timestamp AS timestamp,
  history_value,
  NULL AS forecast_value,
  NULL AS prediction_interval_lower_bound,
  NULL AS prediction_interval_upper_bound
FROM
  (
    SELECT
      PARSE_TIMESTAMP("%Y%m%d", date) AS history_timestamp,
      SUM(totals.visits) AS history_value
    FROM
      `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.${targetTable}`
    GROUP BY date
    ORDER BY date ASC
  )
UNION ALL
SELECT
  forecast_timestamp AS timestamp,
  NULL AS history_value,
  forecast_value,
  prediction_interval_lower_bound,
  prediction_interval_upper_bound
FROM
  ML.FORECAST(MODEL ${bqDataset}.df_ga_time_series_model,
              STRUCT(30 AS horizon, 0.8 AS confidence_level))

#standardSQL
insert into `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_sessions_partitions`
select min(date),1,"Successful" from `bigquery-public-data.google_analytics_sample.ga_sessions_*`
WHERE date = ( SELECT MAX( partitiondate )
                FROM `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_sessions_partitions` )

#standardSQL
update `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_sessions_partitions`
set ingestionstatus="Successful" where partitiondate = (
select min(date) from `bigquery-public-data.google_analytics_sample.ga_sessions_*`
where date="20170601")

insert into `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_sessions_partitions`

WHERE date > ( SELECT MAX( partitiondate )
                FROM `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_sessions_partitions` )

create or replace table `${projectId}.${bqDataset}.df_ga_sessions_partitions` as
